Mandatory fields
How can I terminate my subscription to 100% sports?

100% sports is a subscription service which is automatically renewed every week or day (as appropriate) unless you unsubscribe. You can terminate your subscription whenever you want only by entering in your personal menu on <service URL> (icon at top right of the display) and clicking on Leave 100% sports link. Depending on your mobile operator, you may terminate your subscription by sending a SMS.
Where can I watch all videos?

To watch and enjoy your sports videos, you should simple access to our homepage <homepage link> and click on any video available. You are able to browse our whole catalogue on the main menu (searching by title or category).
I downloaded one sports game but I cannot install it on my handset, what is happening?

First of all, make sure that you have permission to install apps from different stores to Google Play: in your device, go to settings / Security / Device Administration and enable Unknown Sources Allow installation of apps from unknown sources. In addition, you might check if you have enough space in your storage. If this issue persists, don’t hesitate to contact us.
Is it safe to browse videos and download games from 100% sports?
Yes, all content provided by 100% sports is totally safe for your handset and your personal data.
I am subscribed to 100% sports, if I unsubscribe, how much longer will I be able to access videos?

You will keep your access to 100% sports until the last period paid ends. For example, in case of daily subscription which was already renewed today, you will be able to see all videos until current date ends. Or if you were subscribed to weekly and your last renewal happened on Monday, you will have access until Sunday (7 days).
The mobile site does not detect my account and my subscription to 100% sports
Check your 3G or WIFI connection is working properly. If so, and this issue persists, please contact us indicating your issue, phone number, mobile operator and handset.
